name: DATBOI
description: AT BOI is the ultimate meme coin, born from the legendary frog on a unicycle that defined internet absurdity. Here come Dat Boi, rolling into Web3 with unstoppable vibes, dank memes, and a vision for a future where humor drives innovation. Hop on and ride with us! Here comes Dat Boi...
